<H1>Assessors</H1>
<div class=col-md-6>
<table class='cell-border table table-striped table-bordered' cellspacing='0' width='100%'>
  <thead>
    <th>Assessor</th>
    <th>Actions</th>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <% @assessors.each do |assessor| %>
    <tr>
      <td><%= link_to assessor.name, assessor_path(assessor) %></td>
      <td>
        <%= link_to "Show", assessor_path(assessor), class: "btn btn-primary btn-xs"  %>
        <%= link_to "Edit", edit_assessor_path(assessor), class: "btn btn-primary btn-xs"  %>
        <% if policy(assessor).destroy? %>
          <%= link_to "Remove", assessor_path(assessor), method: :delete, data: { confirm: "Are you sure?  This will remove assessor privilges for this resident (but will not delete the resident)" }, class: "btn btn-warning btn-xs" %>
       <% end %>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <% end %>
  </tbody>
</table>
To Create an assessor, edit a <%= link_to "resident", residents_path %> and choose "Make this Resident an Assessor".
</div>
